Package com.taliter.fiscal.device

An API to communicate with fiscal devices.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
FiscalDevice An interface used to communicate with fiscal devices.
FiscalDeviceEventHandler A handler for events that can be triggered by a fiscal device.
FiscalDeviceSource A FiscalDevice factory.
FiscalPacket A request to or response from a fiscal device.
 

Exception Summary
AbortedFiscalRequestException Thrown when a request is aborted.
FiscalDeviceIOException The base class of all fiscal device exceptions.
FiscalDeviceTimeoutException Thrown when a request timeout occurs.
InvalidFiscalResponseException Thrown when an invalid response is received.
 

Package com.taliter.fiscal.device Description

An API to communicate with fiscal devices.
